				<td colspan="2"><span>This is in response to another thread about looking for info.
<br />

<br />
I used to autojoin the Serverwide Bards channel, but there has been too many idots hotkeying spam, and just generally talking about things that I would not want my wife or children to see on my screen if they were looking, so I stop using it.  But I miss having the ability to ask a Bardic question, when needed.
<br />

<br />
What other good, clean, channels are there?
<br />

<br />
Thanks,</span></td>
