				<td colspan="2"><span>;join firiona.molto
<br />

<br />
The only thing we ask if you join our channel, is that in addition to not being foul like people often are in serverwide.bards, please don't brag in the channel either.
<br />

<br />
The last time I invited the whole world to join our channel in a thread like this, some of our Molto regulars were a little mad at me, cause a couple of the people kept linking all their crazy uber gear etc.  Or, if someone mentioned where they were kiting, or where they just got killed, we got a lot of, &quot;well, just pull em to wherever and swarm em, sheesh, that's easy!&quot;  That sort of thing.
<br />

<br />
By all means, if you want friendly bard chat, answers to a bard question, or wanna see what the All Bard guild is up to, please do ;join firiona.molto.
<br />

<br />
Scherzo Glissando <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-17.gif" border="0" alt="" hspace="2" /> 
<br />
Maestro, Molto Espressivo</span></td>
